d 'SUMBAR': module to produce bar charts showing sums of multiple numeric variables with proper labels
d
d  sumbar creates bar charts showing sums of multiple numeric
d variables with proper labels. It can display results as either
d raw sums or percentage distributions, and when used with the by()
d option, creates color-coded grouped bars with clean legends. The
d command is particularly useful for visualizing aggregate data
d across multiple variables where standard approaches may require
d data reshaping and complex syntax. 
d
d KW: graphics
d KW: bar
d KW: charts
d
d Requires: Stata version 11
d
d Distribution-Date: 20250802
d
d Author:   Kabira Namit,  World Bank
d Support: email   knamit@@worldbank.org
d
f stackbar.ado
f stackbar.sthlp
